title: Homework Club
purpose: Homework club is run by a group of Fraser Heights Students who are eager to help out students in various subjects. This club is great for students who'd like extra help on assignments from a knowledgeable peer. It’s a welcoming and warm environment that’s enjoyable for students.
typicalWeek: Students create posters, discuss how to spread the word about the club, and most importantly assist peers with their assignments
schedule: We meet on Monday;Tuesday;Thursdays at Lunchtime. Come Join us!
